{"hash":"7a62437d1d497aa1a5fc67b51faa4ebdae8784f6","data":{"post":{"id":"a2c274881a87f0327ca68a93149dc418","category":"기타","sub_category":"Git","title":"Local 저장소와 Github 연결하기","series_name":"","series_num":0,"content":"<p>local에서 첫 개발을 시작하고 Github repository에 push를 할 단계가 온다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"git-초기화\"><a href=\"#git-%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0%ED%99%94\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Git 초기화</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> init</code></pre>\n<p>위 명령어를 이용하여 git을 초기화한다.</p>\n<p>방금 초기화 했다면 당연히 안되어 있겠지만, </p>\n<p>local 저장소가 원격저장소와 연결되어 있는지 확인한다. </p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"git-remote-연결\"><a href=\"#git-remote-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Git Remote 연결</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote\norigin // 일반적으로 설정하는 원격저장소 이름</code></pre>\n<p>연결되어 있지 않다면 아무것도 뜨지 않는다.</p>\n<p>만들어 둔 github repository를 local 저장소와 연결한다.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote <span class=\"token function\">add</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>remote name<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>github reposit url<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n<p>계정과 비밀번호를 치면 github과 연결되며 이후 일반적인 git명령어를 통해 조작할 수 있다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"git-remote-제거\"><a href=\"#git-remote-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Git Remote 제거</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote remove <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>remote name<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"git-remote-이름-변경\"><a href=\"#git-remote-%EC%9D%B4%EB%A6%84-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Git Remote 이름 변경</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote <span class=\"token function\">rename</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>remote name<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>new remote name<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n","tags":[{"title":"Github","path":"/tag/Github/"},{"title":"Git","path":"/tag/Git/"}],"date":"9월 16 수, 2020","update_date":"9월 16 수, 2020","timeToRead":1,"headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Git 초기화","anchor":"#git-초기화"},{"depth":2,"value":"Git Remote 연결","anchor":"#git-remote-연결"},{"depth":2,"value":"Git Remote 제거","anchor":"#git-remote-제거"},{"depth":2,"value":"Git Remote 이름 변경","anchor":"#git-remote-이름-변경"}]},"related":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"개발자 로드맵 2021","category":"기타","description":"2021 개발자 로드맵 정리","path":"/developer-roadmap-2021/","date":"2021.01.19"}},{"node":{"title":"if(kakao) 2020","category":"기타","description":"if(kakao) 2020 후기","path":"/if-kakao-2020/","date":"2020.12.04"}},{"node":{"title":"Devday 2020","category":"기타","description":"Line Devday2020 후기","path":"/devday-2020/","date":"2020.11.30"}},{"node":{"title":"개발자 로드맵","category":"기타","description":"2020 개발자 로드맵 정리","path":"/developer-roadmap/","date":"2020.10.13"}}]},"series":{"edges":[]}},"context":{}}